title: Saber And Sword  [2006] [L169-DBT]cbr
description:
In a small village lost in the vastness of medieval China, the young and naives Wu Gang challenges kill all the warriors of passage. Taking the technique of the deceased master Fei, he takes on the role of protector of the village against all potential external threats. Until one day an old man armed with a broken sword convinces the young man not to engage. Wu Gang is thus driven from the village and chases the old man to defeat him.

enjoy
